metadata.name: Portal to Sirius
metadata.description:
Through Sirius we learn to dream.
That not everything is as it seems.
Let's spend more time together. 
Let's unpack the deeper layers. 

- Joel Dietz (metalambda.org)


The art piece consists of this poem, custom music composed alongside it, AI art generated by midjourney, and a custom set of extensions developed to create immersive 3d environments called "metalambda."
